---
// Experience section
---

<section id="experience" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 section-spacing reveal">
  <h2 class="h2-divider text-3xl tracking-tight">Experience</h2>
  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-300">Recent roles and impact. Keep it concise for quick scanning.</p>

  <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 border-l border-cyan-400/20 pl-6">
    <article class="reveal rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 to-white/5 p-8 ring-1 ring-blue-400/40">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-3">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">TBO Bank</h3>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-cyan-500/20 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-cyan-300 ring-1 ring-cyan-400/40">
              Current
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Senior Full-Stack Engineer • Feb 2025 – Jan 2026</p>
        </div>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-blue-500/15 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-blue-200 ring-1 ring-blue-400/40">
          Digital Banking Modernization
        </span>
      </div>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-primary"></span>Led full modernization of a white-label platform into a production-grade digital banking system.</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-secondary"></span>Reduced portal load times by ~35% after rebuilding the customer portal with Vue 3 + Vite.</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-tertiary"></span>Integrated high-volume loan lifecycle workflows and operational ticketing systems end-to-end.</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-accent"></span>Hardened backend services with improved validation layers, resiliency, and fault tolerance.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="reveal rounded-3xl card-premium p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Hyphen</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Senior Full-Stack Engineer • Sep 2021 – Feb 2025</p>
        </div>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-blue-500/15 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-blue-200 ring-1 ring-blue-400/40">
          Multi-Brand Fintech Platform
        </span>
      </div>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-primary"></span>Owned and evolved a multi-brand white-label fintech platform across multiple lending products.</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-secondary"></span>Migrated 40+ modules from Vue 2 to Vue 3 + Vite, improving performance and developer velocity.</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-tertiary"></span>Built modular Laravel services integrated with AWS S3, SES, and SQS for scalable async workflows.</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-accent"></span>Replaced legacy SOAP integrations with clean REST APIs, cutting integration complexity significantly.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="reveal rounded-3xl card-premium p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">KAR Global (High Tech Locksmith)</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Senior PHP / Full-Stack Engineer • Jun 2016 – Sep 2021</p>
        </div>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-blue-500/15 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-blue-200 ring-1 ring-blue-400/40">
          CRM & Real-Time Systems
        </span>
      </div>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-primary"></span>Built a proprietary CRM platform from scratch — Laravel, Vue, MySQL, Redis — serving field operations.</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-secondary"></span>Delivered real-time dispatching workflows using Node.js, Socket.io, and Redis pub/sub.</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-tertiary"></span>Designed secure OAuth2 APIs connecting Android mobile apps with Firebase Cloud Messaging.</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-accent"></span>Deployed scalable AWS Lambda microservices, improving backend throughput and reducing infrastructure costs.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="reveal rounded-3xl card-premium p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Freelance & Earlier Roles</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">2008 – 2015 • Symfony/Laravel • Security • Databases</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Built production systems in healthcare, media, and academic institutions using PHP (Symfony, Laravel), MySQL, and
        JavaScript. Designed secure authentication systems and relational databases.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .dot-primary {
    @apply mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full;
    background: var(--c-primary);
  }

  .dot-secondary {
    @apply mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full;
    background: var(--c-secondary);
  }

  .dot-tertiary {
    @apply mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full;
    background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.85);
  }

  .dot-accent {
    @apply mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full;
    background: var(--accent-1);
  }
</style>
